sequenceDiagram
  participant Runtime as Agent runtime
  participant API as OB1 Agent Memory API
  participant DB as OB1 thoughts plus sidecars
  participant Agent as Agent worker

  Runtime->>API: POST /recall with task, scope, entities, limits
  API->>DB: Search thoughts and sidecar policy
  DB-->>API: Candidate memories
  API->>API: Rank by scope, provenance, freshness, confidence
  API-->>Runtime: Memories with use_policy
  Runtime->>Agent: Inject evidence, preferences, or instructions allowed by policy
  Runtime->>API: POST /recall/:id/usage
  API->>DB: Record usage and audit events
